main: ^It is a farm in the town of La Trinidad, province of Benguet, Philippines primarily used for the cultivation of strawberries. It is owned and maintained by the Benguet State University.

c-0: ^People come here to have a glimpse of its lush strawberry farm, have a personal experienceof picking strawberries and buy varying strawberry products.
^Some of these products are strawberry jams, wines, and ice creams. The biggest and most succesful strawberry plantation in the country.
